Adapter Pattern:
Imcompatible Interface to be used is converted to interface expected by Client:
   Class Adapter:
   Object Adapter: Uses Composition to contain the Adaptee into the Adapter( AdapterClass ) Object.
Clinet(Captain)---->expects(BattleShip)-------->   
               ---->BattleShipFishingBoat------->composes of Fishing Boat(Adaptee) as private
